To compile a statically linked binary using an alpine docker image:

docker run --rm -it -v $PWD:/root/src alpine sh -c "apk update; apk add g++ make libpcap-dev; cd /root/src; CXXFLAGS=-DUSE_TCP=1 make pcapsipdump-static"

It should compile to a statically linked binary with the name `pcapsipdump-static`
